'''医用昆虫学'''的研究方向在于影响人类[[健康|健康]]的[[昆虫|昆虫]]和[[节肢动物|节肢动物]]上。医用昆虫学也包括节肢动物疾病的媒介、生态学和流行病学相关的科学研究。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Medical Entomology - an overview {{!}} ScienceDirect Topics|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/agricultural-and-biological-sciences/medical-entomology|accessdate=2020-08-30|work=www.sciencedirect.com}}</ref>

医用昆虫学学家通常被各种各样的机构聘用，如[[大学|大学]]、[[私企|私企]]、[[政府|政府]]等等，<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Robert D. Hall, Medical Entomologist {{!}} Entomological Society of America|url=https://www.entsoc.org/resources/education/hall|accessdate=2020-08-30|work=www.entsoc.org|archive-date=2019-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191217042345/https://www.entsoc.org/resources/education/hall|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外也包括军队也会聘用医用[[昆虫学家|昆虫学家]]以确保军队人员们不会感染节肢动携带的传染病。<ref>{{Cite web|title=U.S. Air Force - Career Detail - Medical Entomologist|url=https://www.airforce.com/careers/detail/medical-entomologist|accessdate=2020-08-30|work=www.airforce.com|archive-date=2017-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170204034531/https://www.airforce.com/careers/detail/medical-entomologist//|dead-url=no}}</ref>昆虫传播的疾病所造成的死亡人数比历史以来所有战争所造成的伤亡的总和还要多。[[化工公司|化工公司]]也会[[聘请|聘请]]医用昆虫学家用以帮助开发更有效、更安全的新型杀虫剂。<ref name=":0" />

